Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.02,0:08:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you yes well she has a question oh speak i have been meditating almost every morning and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,evening for about seven years recently my meditation state is not so good because of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,distracting thoughts i can't enter the meditation state because of distracting thoughts i can't enter
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:09:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the silent and deep state beyond thinkingness sometimes i have been in silent state unexpectedly
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and unintentionally but instantly distracting thoughts break into that state
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and in one sentence in one sentence she's having getting into a very deep meditated state
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,you know she's been meditating a number of years yes and so
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,all of a sudden she has all maybe it's because you have a lot more pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah and so you know you think oh i should be doing the dishes i should be doing this
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:10:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of sitting here and then it's just passing thoughts in order to meditate you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,know you need to know how to compartmentalize your world your life compartmentalize when you're going
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.16,0:10:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to the bathroom you're in one state of consciousness when you're playing in the backyard with the dog
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.61,0:10:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,that's another one
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.08,0:10:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Meditating, that's a totally different one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.94,0:10:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to compartmentalize your life into areas where you're automatically attuned to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,what's in that department in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.14,0:10:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,When you run into the bathroom, you're not worrying about these things, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I try to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So you learn how to compartmentalize your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't expect to be cheerful and happy and skipping around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:11:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But also in a meditative state, don't you see the two don't blend?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.38,0:11:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that simple?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.38,0:11:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Not simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she's still a little confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you confused about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I just explained it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask me a question and then tell me you don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mentally, when you go into meditation, what you need to do is block out all the outside
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Just block it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And say, this is my 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Or 15 minutes for just myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.94,0:11:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And try and block out everything and only concentrate on your inner spiritual being
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,at that point for that length of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn off the television set.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.52,0:11:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It goes on in your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.90,0:11:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you do that, then eventually you will get back into that very deep meditative state.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.26,0:12:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you can turn off that TV while you're meditating, you'll go into that deep state
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.61,0:12:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,like where you want to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.98,0:12:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.98,0:12:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.98,0:12:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Because sometimes you just can't get to that spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.28,0:12:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's easy because I go there all the time and I have to pull myself back to watch
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,television.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,On television, they only have one story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.59,0:12:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They play it around the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Week after week after week.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.99,0:12:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Some killer lady right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.93,0:12:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.93,0:12:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Casey Anthony.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.93,0:12:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.93,0:12:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That plays 24-7.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.93,0:13:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Week after week after week.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.39,0:13:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Same story.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.19,0:13:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What else do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.19,0:13:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help me progress in my meditation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.15,0:13:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.15,0:13:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Just about the meditation was what she wanted to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.15,0:13:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.15,0:13:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
