Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.63,0:13:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.04,0:13:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They want a-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They want what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.46,0:13:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They want a picture and-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:13:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:14:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not sensitive to social cues.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.76,0:14:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You got to perfectly throw them off the stage for them to get to, their time is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.67,0:14:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, translate all this data.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, oh yeah, I'm sorry about that, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You've, I'm glad you reminded me of that fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Myself and some other students of your work have started reading the great books of the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,western world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.50,0:14:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're doing the 10-year reading plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.84,0:14:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.88,0:14:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This month is Adam Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,On what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.12,0:14:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The following month is Karl Marx.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And in Power vs. Force, you have a quote, which I typed out in size 30 font.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.69,0:15:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to read what that states.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to read what this says.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.73,0:15:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If Doc wants to read it and can't hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The extreme negativity of many popular works of pseudo-philosophy, for example,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.79,0:15:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,is obvious if one tests these books.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.37,0:15:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But even being forewarned cannot defend us against unwitting entrainment by negative energy fields,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,which activate when these works are read.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.98,0:15:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,One may think he can maintain his psychic independence by refuting the work intellectually,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.32,0:15:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but mere exposure to the material has profound negative effects that continues
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,even after the materialization.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The material is intellectually rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What material?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.86,0:15:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Karl Marx.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.86,0:15:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.82,0:15:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It is as though there is within these negative influences a hidden virus whose invasion of
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.88,0:16:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,our psyche goes unnoticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.39,0:16:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you suggest we skip Karl Marx this month?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.99,0:16:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to know if you suggest that they skip over Karl Marx in the books of the great
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.41,0:16:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,western world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.41,0:16:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you should know what the world believes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can see why the world believes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Karl Marx had a big impact on the political philosophy of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All of Russia, for instance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That sort of part, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.78,0:16:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.99,0:16:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you should read them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you end up a Marxist, well, you can move to Russia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.72,0:16:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.72,0:16:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:16:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:17:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I need this year to defend myself against Marxists.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.36,0:17:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.60,0:17:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.60,0:17:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to start by saying thank you for staying around so long, for being
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.86,0:17:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.86,0:17:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not up to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.86,0:17:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's God's idea, not mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.44,0:17:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.44,0:17:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thought by just being up here in your presence that I've been here for
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.39,0:17:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.39,0:17:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.39,0:17:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.39,0:17:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I could better come to know how to view all peoples and all creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot hear what she's saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.70,0:17:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it's in God's will, I would also like to have your blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.04,0:17:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:17:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She would like you to give her a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.60,0:18:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She said that coming up here, she thought that she had a better understanding of the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,world around her and the spiritual aspects of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you give her a blessing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.93,0:18:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. I bless you in the name of the Lord, and I thank you for your presence
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.92,0:18:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and your contribution to this meeting. We're coming up here. That takes courage. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.31,0:18:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.26,0:18:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes courage to come up on stage. Yes. I'm scared to death every time I come up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a bag of goodies for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.53,0:18:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping for fresh shrimp. Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:18:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Just chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.54,0:19:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.56,0:19:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you guys for being my teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.34,0:19:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have a question about energy in my navel, which I would consider to be emotional insecurity
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and emotional overwhelm that I experience as emotional overwhelm,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have for maybe 20 years of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.62,0:19:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.86,0:19:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it about everything or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.60,0:19:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Selective?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it happen once a day, twice a day, all day, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes, it can be an exterior event or an interior event,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.48,0:19:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and then it's like I go from high functioning to like emotional overwhelm, where...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.81,0:19:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How often does this happen? I'm trying to get an answer out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.49,0:19:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Every day or all day?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes in waves, sometimes it lasts long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,several weeks I've had one several weeks several weeks like crying weeks weeks
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,like crying crying every day oh and I so I assume that's a stack and I guess it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.46,0:20:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,is I guess I feel stuck because I know if I look at the last 20 years I go that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.66,0:20:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,same experience occurs a powerlessness emotional insecurity and I've I've done
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.70,0:20:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,surrendering surrendering it to God asking for more and yeah uh-huh I still feel like
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.81,0:20:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,like I'm stuck and I guess I'm wondering if there's a deeper subconscious guilt or
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.85,0:20:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,sometimes I feel
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.01,0:21:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,feel when the state comes on like it pulls negative energy like it's both from within and and about me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.39,0:21:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,like um uh it's so i why my question is if is i'm having trouble discerning is this a deeper
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.46,0:21:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,subconscious guilt um is it simply an a an emotional attachment like it's the center of
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.86,0:21:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,my emotional body that i i'm unwilling i get attached to people places and things and then
