Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.10,0:22:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.38,0:22:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not the end of my life so that's the way you have to be with your thoughts and your
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.93,0:22:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,feelings that you value them for what what they serve at the moment and then your willingness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.45,0:22:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to let them go that they have served their purpose there's a time to be very pious and
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,withdraw to the woods and pray on your knees for weeks until they get raggedy but then that time
