Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.85,0:22:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,life has been served then walk away from it with gratitude i thank the oh lord for what was learned
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.18,0:22:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,in that state of consciousness and now i must move on yeah you still have to earn a living you still
