Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.20,0:25:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that go with it you could have seen church bells too you know i mean whatever holiness means to
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.78,0:25:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,a person so a person has a whole energy field called holiness it includes all kinds of symbols
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.29,0:25:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,experiences places historic events and uh it becomes quite sizable in mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.95,0:26:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can summon up portions of it and recently while meditating i um came up with this feel of a
