Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.15,0:26:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,of like you know like static it blocks everything else out i don't know what white noise is
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.14,0:26:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,while meditating but does it keep you in that meditative state yes yes it actually takes me away from my mind to the
