Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.78,0:26:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and put it up on youtube that was a devotional video yeah a devotional video and put it up on
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.82,0:27:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,what youtube yeah yeah so he sent it to us and it's very nice so as we go along uh yeah and i can appreciate
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.20,0:27:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you get a chance to go and look it up, do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.06,0:27:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Look it up where?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.06,0:27:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Online.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.06,0:27:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's on YouTube.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.12,0:27:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I never heard of YouTube.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.44,0:27:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.44,0:27:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a site online that they can post something.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.88,0:27:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What does online mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.56,0:27:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm of a different generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.93,0:27:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Online meant on the clothesline.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.93,0:27:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother would say, hang these online.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.24,0:27:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.26,0:27:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang these online, she'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.08,0:27:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Your white pajamas swinging in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.98,0:27:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.98,0:27:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll never mean the same to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.98,0:27:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,May I have your blessing, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.98,0:27:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he'd like your blessing, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.98,0:27:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you with God's love, amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.98,0:27:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.98,0:27:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,God's love, amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.98,0:28:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.98,0:28:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to touch your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.98,0:28:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a message from you know who.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.42,0:28:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.42,0:28:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.42,0:28:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.58,0:28:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.19,0:28:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.19,0:28:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.74,0:28:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.74,0:28:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.74,0:28:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.74,0:28:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.85,0:28:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.85,0:28:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.85,0:28:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.35,0:28:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.92,0:28:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.92,0:28:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.53,0:28:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.53,0:28:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.85,0:28:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Have I seen you here before?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.85,0:28:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A couple times, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.36,0:28:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you look familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.85,0:28:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.85,0:28:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.85,0:28:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little out of breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.85,0:28:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, my name's Jonathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.58,0:29:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an honor to meet you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.98,0:29:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.34,0:29:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.76,0:29:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, can you hear me okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.36,0:29:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.36,0:29:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I just wanted to thank you both from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.65,0:29:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, your work has changed my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.67,0:29:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.37,0:29:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and I was wondering if we could say the Lord's Prayer together?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.48,0:29:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You want us to say the Lord's Prayer together?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.70,0:29:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.70,0:29:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you know how it goes, lead it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.00,0:29:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.81,0:29:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Lead it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.42,0:29:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Father, who art in heaven, hallowed be thy name.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.24,0:29:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thy kingdom come.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.38,0:29:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thy will be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.12,0:29:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,On earth as it is in heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.76,0:29:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Give us this day our daily bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.58,0:29:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And forgive us our trespasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.88,0:30:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,As we forgive those who trespass against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.46,0:30:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And lead us not into temptation.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.02,0:30:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But deliver us from evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.08,0:30:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,For thine is the kingdom and the power and the glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.62,0:30:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever and ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.12,0:30:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.00,0:30:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.30,0:30:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, David.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.30,0:30:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.40,0:30:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is transformative.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.14,0:30:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We try to.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.06,0:30:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,At all times, you know, move into a field of compassion and love for all that exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.38,0:30:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Compassion and love for all that exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.96,0:30:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We see this lion kill the baby rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.71,0:30:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And the mind says, oh, bad lion.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.75,0:30:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad lion.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.85,0:30:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But the lion has to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.29,0:31:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And if lions didn't eat rabbits, there wouldn't be any rabbits.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.29,0:31:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Because rabbits come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.40,0:31:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So lions have something.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.96,0:31:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.57,0:31:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,People are born in order to pay taxes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.12,0:31:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The government is against birth control, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.76,0:31:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.62,0:31:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.62,0:31:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thank you for your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.30,0:31:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been, your books have been very helpful to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.96,0:31:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.30,0:31:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've, to use your own term, I've been in the midst of a final run.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.78,0:31:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And find myself impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.02,0:31:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And would just ask for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.68,0:31:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Some word of encouragement, it's a.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.80,0:31:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes you think you're in the final run?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.29,0:31:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I've dedicated every moment to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.84,0:32:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.04,0:32:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're serious about your spiritual commitment.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.90,0:32:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.36,0:32:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.17,0:32:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.93,0:32:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can't really lay out a period of time and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.88,0:32:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,this is when the final run starts and this is when the final run ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.24,0:32:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, this.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.44,0:32:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This lifetime you're born at a certain level of consciousness and with karmic
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.96,0:32:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,factors involved, you may choose to move on or you may choose to skip it this
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.23,0:32:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,lifetime and move on some later time, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.34,0:32:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So I would not be self-critical about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.57,0:32:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I would just ask God to reveal to me the purpose of, the primary purpose of this
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.25,0:32:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,time and this lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.34,0:32:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.99,0:32:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.67,0:32:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.98,0:33:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.86,0:33:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is related to an experience I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.46,0:33:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was on an extended meditation retreat and I had taken vows and surrendered my life to
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.80,0:33:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,God and during that retreat, we were to learn a special technique and out of pride as well
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.20,0:33:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,as just not being open to stop getting the technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.18,0:33:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I received the technique before.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.16,0:33:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm having trouble understanding him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.56,0:33:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You were on a retreat, which was devoted.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.08,0:33:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,To what?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.80,0:33:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,To God.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.32,0:33:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak slowly, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.74,0:33:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.30,0:33:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Devoted to, of course, I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.98,0:33:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and it was essentially a meditation retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.92,0:33:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A meditation retreat, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.52,0:33:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And I, to receive a special meditation technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.84,0:33:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.34,0:34:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And I received it, I was told that if you receive it too early, that you can actually
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.29,0:34:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,totally mess up your ability to be, have a continuous experience of the silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.34,0:34:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.72,0:34:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.32,0:34:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try and paraphrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.76,0:34:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run on.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.41,0:34:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.43,0:34:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What he's saying, the teaching is false.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.36,0:34:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.86,0:34:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.34,0:34:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So, essentially, I've been doing the 12 steps and there's just, I've released this and I've
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.94,0:34:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,spoke about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.11,0:34:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So, essentially, that belief is incorrect is what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.08,0:34:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.56,0:34:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what the arm says.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.64,0:34:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't quote me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.13,0:34:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.46,0:34:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.24,0:35:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, because the, essentially, my question is, the belief is around the fact that in
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.18,0:35:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that experience, I had forsaken my relationship with God in this life.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.64,0:35:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you get that message from?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.64,0:35:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,From, from what happened during the experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.64,0:35:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It was more an internal thing, not so much from others.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.64,0:35:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But, essentially, since that point, I've been meditating a lot, doing spiritual work, and
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.68,0:35:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,my experience continues to evolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.08,0:35:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I have a belief that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.24,0:35:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a belief that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.26,0:35:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, I believe I have a block to experiencing the silence continually all the time, which
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.84,0:35:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is what I'd like to, is to experience the presence of God at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.18,0:35:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a, I feel that I have a block to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.93,0:35:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I just wondered if you have any advice for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.53,0:35:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to experience the presence of God at all times, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.51,0:35:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.71,0:35:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.83,0:35:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, why don't you just do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.48,0:36:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.80,0:36:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay no attention to the passing streetcars, and the passing women, and people dangling
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.58,0:36:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,money in front of your nose for one thing or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.25,0:36:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep in mind that God, it prevails at all times, and in all places, and in all situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.27,0:36:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The presence of God is continuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.82,0:36:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like the weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.14,0:36:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stop now and notice the sunshine is shining, or not notice it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.64,0:36:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But, whether you notice it or not doesn't affect the fact that you're in the right place.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.64,0:36:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a matter of what you want to focus on, what you want to look at.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.80,0:36:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can look at the quietude in this room, or I can look at the sun coming in the windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.18,0:36:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.80,0:37:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's not God coming up and then disappearing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.94,0:37:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just noticing what you notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.88,0:37:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you accept life as you experience it unfolding.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.23,0:37:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Right at this moment, you are here talking to me, and within a few seconds, you'll be
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.03,0:37:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,out in the room going that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.09,0:37:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And, that's the way it's supposed to be, continuous change, and movement, and et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.03,0:37:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you tell yourself, that's normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.23,0:37:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what's desirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.91,0:37:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If God wanted it to be different, it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.46,0:37:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.12,0:37:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If God wanted it to be different, it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.17,0:37:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Simple enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.74,0:37:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.81,0:37:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I shake your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.08,0:38:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.02,0:38:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.71,0:38:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If God wanted things to be different, they would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.48,0:38:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We came here to become enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.58,0:38:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If we were enlightened, we wouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.26,0:38:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we don't have to feel ashamed that we're not enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.16,0:38:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We come here to become so.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.36,0:38:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,To move us along the pathway.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.11,0:38:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.73,0:38:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you ohm for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.35,0:38:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.67,0:38:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you do an ohm?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.20,0:38:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.24,0:38:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You want a big ohm or a little ohm?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.20,0:38:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.94,0:38:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do a big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.92,0:38:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a big ohm.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.20,0:38:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, golly whizzer.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.19,0:38:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.89,0:39:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,May I also shake your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.75,0:39:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And yours too, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.45,0:39:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.05,0:39:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to touch your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.73,0:39:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.15,0:39:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The last time I was up here, I was a little too nervous to look into the doc's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.89,0:39:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if I could look into his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.94,0:40:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear what he's saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.18,0:40:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.80,0:40:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.35,0:40:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.99,0:40:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.47,0:40:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I said the window to the cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.02,0:40:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.86,0:40:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.98,0:40:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.30,0:40:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here to offer my prostration.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.14,0:40:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And receive your blessings.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.58,0:40:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please allow me to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.04,0:40:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a monk?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.86,0:40:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.40,0:40:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,From where?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.01,0:40:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,From India.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.83,0:40:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.52,0:40:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Better the cow when they're from India.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.89,0:40:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.32,0:41:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.51,0:41:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's harder to be a monk in the world than out of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.64,0:41:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.66,0:41:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I would like to thank you for all your teachings.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.70,0:41:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question about the connection between selfless service.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.72,0:41:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and the inner work they're both the same so then the question is when i see something happens in
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.14,0:41:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the world and i there's a response coming from inside my mind do i have to recontextualize
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.66,0:42:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and or recontextualize and do something about it when you see something does have to
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.23,0:42:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,recontextualize it or an induced act on it or oh it depends on where he is in the evolution of his
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.47,0:42:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,spirit i think it's god's problem see you may figure you got to help the streetcar get back
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.19,0:42:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,on the track and i figure it's god's problem so where is the selfless service uh where is the
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.21,0:42:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,service coming to picture if i contextually contextualize it as a god's problem where do i
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.46,0:42:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,act
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.68,0:42:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,when you give yeah selfless service and inner work and you said it's one and the same so
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.54,0:42:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,when does he do the selfless service uh and um be of service to the world at all times there
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.00,0:43:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't any separation of the two if i don't see a problem where do i serve if yeah so he's looking
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.56,0:43:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,for a problem no that's that's defective looking for problems is not the way to find out
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.36,0:43:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,anything about anything so selfless service should be done with without a heavy heart it
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.08,0:43:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,should be done with an open heart yes and uh it's artificial to like look for a problem
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.50,0:43:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,i mean what do you think is a problem is in your head there aren't any problems in the world so we
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.54,0:43:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,just sit and meditate what well you know in ashrams there's always things that need to be done
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.34,0:43:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.06,0:44:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you know so that's selfless service but oh but so that's what he's saying is he says do you just
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.92,0:44:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,sit and meditate and just ask or is there when do you uh respond so he has a conflict between
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.13,0:44:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,uh striving for enlightenment right and service to the world that's an artificial dichotomy there
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.67,0:44:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,is no difference between the two you know you can be sweeping the street and uh
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.03,0:44:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,or sitting cross-legged and meditating they're both the same sweeping the street is the same so
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.84,0:44:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,in other words he can be service whether he's sweeping the street or whether he's meditating
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.24,0:44:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,he's still service to the world well he's defining service in what he calls service
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.36,0:44:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,right so then he it's just the definition he makes up if he thinks this is a service to the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.30,0:45:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,world and that serves to the world but if i say it's irrelevant to the world then it's not service
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.02,0:45:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,anymore, right? So service to the world is whatever you define as service to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.32,0:45:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Keeping out of the way and staying silent is the best way.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.32,0:45:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I have one more question. When I witness the thoughts, how do I take the next step from
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.18,0:45:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,witnessing to the next deeper state?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.58,0:45:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the next deeper state? There isn't any deeper state. Witnessing is what's happening
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.91,0:45:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,all the time. The mind is doing witnessing all the time. It doesn't need you to tell
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.32,0:45:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,it to go ahead and witness. The lights go on. You notice that the lights go on. You
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.59,0:45:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't notice that the lights go on. You didn't notice that the lights go on. You didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.75,0:46:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,say to your mind, mind please watch and notice whether the lights go on. It's happening spontaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.15,0:46:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't have to do anything about it because that's what the mind is doing automatically
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.00,0:46:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,because of its quality. So just let the mind do what it does. It just notices things spontaneously
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.86,0:46:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and autonomously. So we allow the mind to just be autonomously
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.20,0:46:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that which it is already and it doesn't need your help to be told what to do. You don't
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.26,0:46:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,have to tell your mind to notice everything going on around here. That's what it's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.52,0:46:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything else that needs to be done?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.88,0:47:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You keep pushing for something to do. Let go of d-o. Just be! OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.21,0:47:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I would seek blessings from you on my spiritual journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.95,0:47:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you on your spiritual journey. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.98,0:47:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Call the police. God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.74,0:47:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.52,0:47:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to ask something in my mind. Give me your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.77,0:47:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.95,0:47:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, I'm from India.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.11,0:47:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from India.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.31,0:47:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She's from India?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.86,0:47:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.80,0:47:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been in this country for the last about 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.34,0:48:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And yesterday was a very significant day in our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.92,0:48:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called Guru Purnima.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.94,0:48:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's called in India.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.84,0:48:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm having a terrible time hearing today.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.60,0:48:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Guru is Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.26,0:48:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Purnima yesterday was a full moon day where we have tribute to Guru Parampara.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.40,0:48:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just here to seek your blessings since it was only yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.60,0:48:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And I love you, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.25,0:48:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.24,0:48:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless India.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.46,0:48:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times have we lived in India already?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.74,0:48:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate to think of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.20,0:48:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We rotate through India.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.51,0:48:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,India is like spiritual headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.70,0:48:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We've all probably lived 20, 30 lives in India.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.66,0:49:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid to go back to India because he said the same thing when I was here last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.90,0:49:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.64,0:49:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he's going to kiss Shiva or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.24,0:49:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.94,0:49:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a great country.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.12,0:49:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.84,0:49:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.45,0:49:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to say thanks for the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.26,0:49:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,On step 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.48,0:49:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there any techniques we can do to help us discern God's will versus the ego's will?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.21,0:49:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the ego is always looking for gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.63,0:49:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And God looks to what isness.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.75,0:49:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego is always looking for what it can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.42,0:49:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And that helps differentiate.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.06,0:50:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So, spiritual states are a way of being.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.60,0:50:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're not concerned with getting.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.45,0:50:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the 11th step again?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.73,0:50:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it through prayer and meditation.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.96,0:50:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We pray for the knowledge of his will and the power to carry that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.60,0:50:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.14,0:50:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's easy enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.44,0:50:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear God, we pray for the conscious awareness and knowledge of your will for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.08,0:50:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the capacity to fulfill that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.17,0:50:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's simple and self-explanatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.44,0:50:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.64,0:51:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Namaste, Dr. Hawking.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.15,0:51:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Namaste.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.15,0:51:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.54,0:51:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.54,0:51:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.54,0:51:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, help.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.54,0:51:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.54,0:51:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.54,0:51:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When I finally met you, there was a knowingness that came about that my search is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.10,0:51:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.10,0:51:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why would you recommend we do Course of Miracles, Gita, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.86,0:51:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I recommend it for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.86,0:51:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.14,0:51:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,For her?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.14,0:51:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.14,0:51:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,For her?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.14,0:51:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.14,0:51:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,For her?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.46,0:51:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.46,0:51:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,For her?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.48,0:51:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.48,0:51:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.48,0:51:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.48,0:51:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.48,0:51:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.48,0:51:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.48,0:51:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.48,0:51:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.48,0:51:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.48,0:51:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.44,0:51:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.44,0:51:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.44,0:51:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.43,0:51:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.69,0:51:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.69,0:51:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what was the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.69,0:51:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the question is, if your teachings, which I feel, are the ultimate, and I feel
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.98,0:52:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,so complete having found your teachings, then why do I need to study anybody else?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.79,0:52:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.09,0:52:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why do you recommend Course of Miracles, Ramana, or Gita?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.21,0:52:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.21,0:52:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's alternate ways to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.79,0:52:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I'm not the only source of truth in the history of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.21,0:52:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel that you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.30,0:52:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, because various spiritual pathways are appropriate for different times in our spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.18,0:52:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.18,0:52:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a period of searching and becoming familiar with the field and trying to find
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.82,0:52:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,what fits for you, and each one adds another layer of comprehension and depth of understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.15,0:52:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So there are things that are unique to A Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.01,0:52:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There's things that are unique to Christianity.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.51,0:52:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There's things that are unique to Judaism.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.33,0:53:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Each of them have a contribution to make, because the totality of spiritual knowledge
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.11,0:53:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and understanding is pretty voluminous, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.67,0:53:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, you would think the Vatican's library is useless, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.34,0:53:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No, man has been studying this subject and meditating on it and fasting and satiating.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.04,0:53:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.04,0:53:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And sacrificing and doing all kinds of things to increase his conscious awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.62,0:53:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,of the presence of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.30,0:53:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And I suppose when we reach a certain degree of understanding, we don't reincarnate.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.95,0:53:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.95,0:53:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.95,0:53:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Bodhisattva path.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.48,0:53:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.21,0:53:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.66,0:53:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.66,0:53:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.98,0:53:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.98,0:54:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.28,0:54:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your teachings, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.28,0:54:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.28,0:54:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.28,0:54:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.28,0:54:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.28,0:54:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.28,0:54:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.08,0:54:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is in case of when we are getting older and in case of illnesses, we have many
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.75,0:54:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,medications on the market, but also going back where you say on your books that one
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.63,0:54:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,could do many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.87,0:54:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.87,0:54:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.87,0:54:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there are many medications to get from home remedies or anything to get as
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.87,0:54:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,well.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.32,0:55:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But my question is, there is some medications that do more harm than good.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.25,0:55:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There is osteoporosis medications that have many side effects, and my question is what's
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.17,0:55:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,your advice on that particular subject?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.29,0:55:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.29,0:55:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.29,0:55:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you so much for your questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.25,0:55:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to take it or not to take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.49,0:55:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.03,0:55:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She said there's several, for her, there is osteoporosis medication,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.87,0:55:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and she was wondering what your advice would be to her for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.41,0:55:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,which is, you know, everything's mental, spiritual, and physical.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.76,0:55:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.02,0:55:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She has osteoporosis?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.39,0:55:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and they have medications that they're asking her to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.72,0:55:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Medications, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.92,0:55:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But she does have side effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.32,0:55:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, what does she mean by a side effect?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.67,0:56:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Bleeding, bone, muscle pain, swollen tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.84,0:56:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You have osteoporosis?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.92,0:56:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.62,0:56:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.57,0:56:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a calcium deficiency?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.00,0:56:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.08,0:56:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.56,0:56:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.56,0:56:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you take calcium, that cures it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.94,0:56:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.45,0:56:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,if you could take,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.87,0:56:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,if you should take the medications where they said the medication is good,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.61,0:56:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,it reverses the osteoporosis,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.99,0:56:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,but the side effects do a lot of harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.11,0:56:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.23,0:56:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's his advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.51,0:56:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The question is, should she take medication for osteoporosis or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.49,0:56:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What medication?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.95,0:56:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She has osteoporosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.63,0:56:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.95,0:57:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're suggesting that she takes,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.03,0:57:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,she's taking this medication that has a lot of side effects and she's afraid of the side effects of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.67,0:57:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, oh, stop there, stop there, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.02,0:57:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.28,0:57:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's safe for you to take that.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.86,0:57:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.00,0:57:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's safe for you to take the medication, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.09,0:57:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I shake your hand, Dr. Hacking?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.37,0:57:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Osteoporosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.15,0:57:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take one more question and then we'll take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.20,0:57:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Osteoporosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.58,0:57:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.58,0:57:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Osteoporosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.53,0:57:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Holds in the bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.37,0:57:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's two with one.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.64,0:57:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.10,0:57:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.80,0:57:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.74,0:57:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.46,0:57:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.30,0:57:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Big trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.24,0:57:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Big problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.64,0:57:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.86,0:58:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.54,0:58:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, she has one question about her dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.44,0:58:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Her dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.08,0:58:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.38,0:58:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.02,0:58:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.28,0:58:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She had a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.26,0:58:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.54,0:58:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She just asked a question about her dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.02,0:58:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.80,0:58:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, actually, I mean, 17 years ago, she had a kind of four-year treatment about psychosocial,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.70,0:58:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, psychoanalysis treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.92,0:58:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.12,0:58:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Psychoanalysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.28,0:58:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Psychoanalysis, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.38,0:58:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, psychoanalysis treatment for her psychological problem, and then she learned that kind of
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.87,0:58:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,procedure as well, and then several years later, she has another kind of big, big kind
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.51,0:58:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,of event for her life, and then she suffered that kind of experience, and then later on,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.93,0:58:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and then she learned about Dr. Hopkins and his book, and then he learned a lot, and then
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.58,0:58:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,later on, in her dream, physical dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.38,0:58:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He showed up, and kind of tried to resolve some issue, and then one of them, and then
