Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.94,1:10:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to hold in mind a family member to be calibrated, if that's possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.94,1:10:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't want to do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.16,1:10:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.71,1:10:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.15,1:10:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,May I have a handshake?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.67,1:10:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.87,1:10:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a handshake?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.43,1:10:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.23,1:10:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.53,1:10:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.99,1:10:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.00,1:10:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably had his mother-in-law in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.28,1:11:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty close.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.85,1:11:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.98,1:11:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pleasure to be here with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.32,1:11:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.62,1:11:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been such an incredible inspiration to me, and I'm a 12-stepper, and your work
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.94,1:11:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,has meant so much to me in that venue.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.46,1:11:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.94,1:11:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about Robert Monroe's last work.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.76,1:11:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe it's called...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.38,1:11:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,About who?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.02,1:11:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Robert Monroe.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.58,1:11:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And his last work...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.44,1:11:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called The Ultimate Journey.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.68,1:11:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't recall it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.96,1:11:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The Out-of-Body Experiences?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.44,1:11:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't recall it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.83,1:11:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Robert Monroe?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.41,1:12:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't recall it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.21,1:12:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's his last book.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.69,1:12:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't recall it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.39,1:12:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.23,1:12:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in it, he talks about the physical universe, and he also talks about the non-physical,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.19,1:12:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and he says that in the physical universe, in their explorations of the physical universe,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.63,1:12:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,they run into no intelligent alien species.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.05,1:12:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Whereas in the non-physical universe...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.83,1:12:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't answer your question.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.25,1:12:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't answer my question?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.85,1:12:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is about the...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.37,1:12:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Robert Monroe wrote a book.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.45,1:12:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the name of the book?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.49,1:12:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He wrote...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.47,1:12:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Journeys Out of the Body.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.63,1:12:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Journeys Out of the Body.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.21,1:12:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He wrote three.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.13,1:12:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.89,1:12:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.47,1:12:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The third one...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.13,1:12:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by three?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.79,1:12:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Three.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.09,1:12:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Three books.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.90,1:12:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I only know Journeys Out of the Body.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.22,1:13:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The last one is called Ultimate Journey.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.28,1:13:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.44,1:13:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.88,1:13:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in it, he talks about intelligent species that are within the non-physical universe,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.88,1:13:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and their significance in terms of your own, or my own, I would suppose, pursuit of those kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.73,1:13:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to know the answer to that one.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.78,1:13:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't need to know the answer to that one.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.86,1:13:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.26,1:13:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.02,1:13:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.64,1:13:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.54,1:13:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My answer to him was correct, Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.86,1:13:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.14,1:13:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.94,1:13:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to know everything that was written since the beginning of time, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.39,1:13:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to know everything that was ever written since the beginning of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.40,1:13:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I gave it up as a hopeless addiction.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.02,1:14:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a very...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.34,1:14:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned speed reading as a kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.07,1:14:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I always read a book a day.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.47,1:14:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I read 400 books a year for decades.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.02,1:14:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,400 books a year for decades.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.42,1:14:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So, for one...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.20,1:14:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,For one decade, that's 4,000 books.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.34,1:14:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,For two decades, that's 8,000 books.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.18,1:14:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And I sneaked in a couple thousand on the side for amusement.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.03,1:14:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So, my intellect has been fortified by the intellectual content of 10,000 books.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.22,1:14:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.51,1:14:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to quit reading.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.02,1:14:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.52,1:14:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to thank you both for your dedication to the work.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.82,1:14:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's touched all of our lives significantly.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.26,1:14:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would like to bless you and hold your hand, if possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.45,1:15:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Cold, wet hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.83,1:15:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.51,1:15:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, oh boy, you have cold, wet hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.91,1:15:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You better hold them in a tub of warm water.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.53,1:15:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.39,1:15:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Try friction.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.95,1:15:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Friction, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.07,1:15:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.55,1:15:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Friction.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.25,1:15:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.79,1:15:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't go away.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.54,1:15:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.38,1:15:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.60,1:15:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.84,1:15:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now let's feel them.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.78,1:15:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's feel them.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.18,1:15:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's better.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.08,1:15:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.13,1:15:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Still chilly, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.29,1:15:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, honey, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.58,1:15:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.84,1:15:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.30,1:16:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He's from Korea, and there are people in the Dr. Hawkins study group
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.96,1:16:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that were not able to come today,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.40,1:16:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're asking you to send them a special blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.98,1:16:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I will do so right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.17,1:16:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear God, amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.31,1:16:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I send a special blessing to these, thy children, and my brothers.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.33,1:16:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.13,1:16:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.53,1:16:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought we'd be going back to Korea,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.31,1:16:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,when they got supersonic jets,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.75,1:16:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but they never developed the supersonic jets.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.36,1:16:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.20,1:16:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.04,1:16:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.29,1:16:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, how does one get over approval-seeking?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.87,1:16:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How does one get over what?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.09,1:16:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Approval-seeking.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.14,1:17:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeking the approvals of others.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.92,1:17:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.40,1:17:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a type of ego thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.72,1:17:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it sure is ego, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.44,1:17:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing but ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.32,1:17:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.86,1:17:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.84,1:17:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.72,1:17:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is the answer to just about everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.42,1:17:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And you don't need other people's approval when you love yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.28,1:17:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and when you love everything and everyone around you
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.92,1:17:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,because love is its own reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.14,1:17:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether people love me while I give this talk here in front of the group is irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.39,1:17:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,My service is to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.39,1:17:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And I serve God by serving myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.72,1:17:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I serve my fellow man and all that lives.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.55,1:17:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, I don't step on the bug on the sidewalk
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.53,1:17:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,because it has life and I respect life
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.85,1:18:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and life to me is the expression of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.84,1:18:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't want to step on God.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.92,1:18:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I walk around the bug.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.00,1:18:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.69,1:18:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of devotion to God and realizing that love is God,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.00,1:18:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that solves all problems.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.60,1:18:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you're less than perfect,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.89,1:18:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,uh, uh,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.25,1:18:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not permissible to beat up on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.85,1:18:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That is not permissible.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.25,1:18:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.77,1:18:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No beating on yourself for not being perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.17,1:18:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.34,1:18:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,To not be perfect is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.12,1:18:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were perfect, you wouldn't be a human being.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.38,1:18:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd stay in heaven and wouldn't have made a trip here.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.08,1:18:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So I say thank you, God, for whatever lessons have been learned.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.78,1:18:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.70,1:18:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,everything is a gift from God.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.42,1:18:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is a gift from God.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.30,1:18:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.08,1:18:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.09,1:19:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.11,1:19:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.11,1:19:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.02,1:19:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a good question.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.32,1:19:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.50,1:19:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a good question.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.62,1:19:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Something I haven't made clear, apparently, in the lectures.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.06,1:19:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything that exists is God.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.46,1:19:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing can exist except God.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.60,1:19:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Existence is solely the realm of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.83,1:19:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.70,1:19:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.84,1:19:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't really have a question today.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.30,1:19:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just here to...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.56,1:19:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.04,1:20:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask your blessing and guidance on the path.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.58,1:20:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.07,1:20:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to ask your blessing...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.07,1:20:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.07,1:20:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...and guidance on the...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.52,1:20:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And what?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.10,1:20:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...and guidance on the path.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.10,1:20:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't give him guidance on the path.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.10,1:20:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd have to be your spiritual counselor.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.10,1:20:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know where the hell you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.19,1:20:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe you are my spiritual counselor, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.19,1:20:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you in chapter 1?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.19,1:20:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.19,1:20:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're here at one of these lectures, that's pretty advanced already.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.19,1:20:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.69,1:20:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Because our lectures don't appeal to the average person in the world, I don't think.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.11,1:20:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.42,1:20:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They're too erudite, you might say.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.42,1:20:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't understand them.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.42,1:20:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's a total joy and just unspeakable love to be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.00,1:20:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.00,1:20:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a total joy, he said.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.12,1:20:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.12,1:21:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.60,1:21:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, yes. Thank you, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.60,1:21:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.36,1:21:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.36,1:21:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.16,1:21:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.80,1:21:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go to grad school to be a therapist.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.18,1:21:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question is, is that an appropriate path for me?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.18,1:21:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.18,1:21:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You chose it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.50,1:21:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.50,1:21:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What more do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.50,1:21:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, is the school that I'm choosing in the highest good?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.50,1:21:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have that question if it's in alignment.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.50,1:21:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to fuss job me now.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.50,1:21:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What she's doing is correct, and the school is fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.04,1:21:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.04,1:21:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, no, thank you for the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.40,1:21:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand what you meant.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.40,1:22:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody wants to know, am I doing the right thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.40,1:22:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.42,1:22:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Every thinking person really wonders that.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.42,1:22:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I doing the right thing, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.42,1:22:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I be doing something else?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.04,1:22:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I give up booze and women or not, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.81,1:22:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up booze and women for God, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.12,1:22:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to thank you, Doctor and Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.12,1:22:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first read your book, Power Versus Force, my actual proof was that I actually went out.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.54,1:22:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a jazz composer, and I went out and wrote three of the best tunes that I've ever written.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.67,1:22:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You wrote a nice tune?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.67,1:22:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Three.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.67,1:22:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Three tunes?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.67,1:22:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Three tunes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.67,1:22:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They just came out.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.67,1:22:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Dum, dum, dum.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.83,1:22:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.83,1:22:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so my question actually concerns my son.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.18,1:23:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,About a year and a half ago, he came to you, and my son's name is Brian, and he was embarrassed
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.52,1:23:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,about living with his folks still.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.52,1:23:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty-five or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.90,1:23:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty-five, and he's still living with the folks at home?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.90,1:23:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.90,1:23:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.90,1:23:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.90,1:23:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And you told him in no uncertain terms to get his act together and go get a job, for
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.96,1:23:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,all of you who remember this, and said, you know, it's pretty cushy there, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.04,1:23:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But what's happened since hasn't been so fortunate.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.14,1:23:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He always had respiratory problems, severe respiratory problems.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.14,1:23:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then after he talked to you, he went through a year where he was in three different mental
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.33,1:23:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,psychiatric wards for diagnosis of schizophrenic.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.40,1:24:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.40,1:24:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And since then, he's gotten out and is doing his respiratory.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.40,1:24:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The psych...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.40,1:24:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The schizophrenic...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.16,1:24:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mixing two problems, respiratory and schizophrenia.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.16,1:24:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they may be connected, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.16,1:24:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not connected.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.16,1:24:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so he's gone now from his schizophrenia to respiratory, back to respiratory problems,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.29,1:24:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's still not working.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.29,1:24:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.29,1:24:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He does a lot of 12-step work.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.29,1:24:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just wondering how I can best assist him in a recovery that's real.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.22,1:24:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, recovery from what?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.22,1:24:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Respiratory.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.44,1:24:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Respiratory.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.44,1:24:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a strictly physical problem, correct?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.44,1:24:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Medicine?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.44,1:24:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.44,1:24:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he doesn't do yoga for it, does he?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.44,1:24:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.53,1:24:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So what does he do for his respiratory problem?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.53,1:24:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you his father?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.33,1:24:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm his father.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.33,1:24:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.33,1:24:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And he lives with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.59,1:24:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.59,1:24:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And he lives with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.59,1:24:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.59,1:24:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You must know, what does he do for his respiratory problem?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.59,1:24:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he take medicine?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.59,1:25:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.59,1:25:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He takes...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.59,1:25:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.59,1:25:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And he also takes...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.59,1:25:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he's taking Luxapro for...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.59,1:25:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.59,1:25:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He's taking...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.59,1:25:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.59,1:25:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.59,1:25:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.59,1:25:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.59,1:25:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.59,1:25:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.59,1:25:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He takes...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.59,1:25:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He takes...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.59,1:25:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He takes...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.59,1:25:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He's taking...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.59,1:25:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He's taking...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.59,1:25:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure what he takes for his mental problems.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.59,1:25:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.59,1:25:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Asked you one thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.59,1:25:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked you about his respiratory problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.59,1:25:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you answer me about his mental problem?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.59,1:25:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked you about his lung problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.59,1:25:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.59,1:25:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.59,1:25:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you focus on that?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.59,1:25:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what he takes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.59,1:25:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.59,1:25:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.59,1:25:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,For his mental problem, he takes an anti-schizophrenia drug.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.09,1:25:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He takes Luxapro, which is an antidepressant.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.27,1:25:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, an antidepressant?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.37,1:25:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.37,1:25:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.37,1:25:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So how is he doing on that?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.24,1:25:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He's stabilized.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.24,1:25:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.24,1:25:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.84,1:25:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's improved, you mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.12,1:25:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, he has.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.04,1:25:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's improved, same as.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.70,1:25:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And he does a lot of 12-step, he leads a lot of 12-step groups.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.78,1:25:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, great, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.76,1:25:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's your question now?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.96,1:26:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how can I assist him into getting, you know, work, getting him into the real world?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.11,1:26:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is it this is something I just have to lay hands off and, you know, pray?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.46,1:26:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, hands off, resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.97,1:26:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll do whatever he's going to do spontaneously.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.93,1:26:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.99,1:26:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you very much, really.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.08,1:26:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,When a rabbit needs a better hole, he goes and gets a better hole, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.03,1:26:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, rabbit, run.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.96,1:26:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.05,1:26:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we all love, we love rabbits.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.23,1:26:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I love rabbits.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.10,1:26:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people shoot them and eat them, but I love them.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.64,1:26:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.14,1:26:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I had this dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.04,1:26:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.38,1:27:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she's talking.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.74,1:27:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.96,1:27:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.56,1:27:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She had this dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.44,1:27:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.06,1:27:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.64,1:27:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.53,1:27:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she was kidding.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.79,1:27:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.23,1:27:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get here, let me know.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.19,1:27:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring your mind with you when you come up here, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.75,1:27:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Make a joke.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.67,1:27:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.09,1:27:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.53,1:27:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if I could get you to sign.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.13,1:27:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.53,1:27:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you sign this, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.85,1:27:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.09,1:27:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You should sign the picture, if you would.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.36,1:27:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one of those.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.12,1:27:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't got a pen or what do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.06,1:27:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.54,1:27:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You sign it, please, please, please, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.16,1:27:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Your signature.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.21,1:27:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.85,1:27:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.02,1:28:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's this handsome-looking man and this beautiful woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.08,1:28:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear, oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.28,1:28:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.78,1:28:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.66,1:28:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.16,1:28:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.76,1:28:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Handsome is as handsome does, my mother used to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.80,1:28:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandmother used to say that.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.10,1:28:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty is as pretty does.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.52,1:28:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.02,1:28:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, handsome, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.37,1:28:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you happen to have any ideas about how acupuncture works?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.10,1:28:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about acupuncture?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.66,1:28:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.69,1:28:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.69,1:28:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How does it work?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.69,1:28:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.69,1:28:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it bad?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.69,1:28:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How does it work?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.32,1:28:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It works fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.32,1:28:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Human experience and ingenuity is developed over the centuries.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.00,1:28:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Some parts of the world is very advanced.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.84,1:28:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had a lot of things cured by acupuncture.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.95,1:28:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Acupuncture has cured a lot of things in me, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.87,1:29:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He had an ulcer, a bleeding ulcer, and when it first came to the US, he had it treated
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.38,1:29:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,with acupuncture.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.12,1:29:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And diverticulitis.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.12,1:29:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I had it treated with acupuncture.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.96,1:29:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.96,1:29:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.05,1:29:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And other diseases I forgot, migraine headaches, all kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.05,1:29:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, acupuncture, I'm a big enthusiast about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.21,1:29:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not totally, it's just, it's not like, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.40,1:29:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If they hit the right point, you'll know.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.39,1:29:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.39,1:29:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I studied acupuncture, and I'm familiar with it, its use, and I've seen it useful
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.15,1:29:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,for people.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.15,1:29:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I just never had an explanation of the mechanism.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.39,1:29:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How does it work?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.39,1:29:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wondered if you had any ideas.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.39,1:29:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She's asking me, how does it work?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.39,1:29:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.39,1:29:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how it works.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.39,1:29:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.39,1:29:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.39,1:29:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How does the nervous system work?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.39,1:29:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the analogous to the nervous system.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.39,1:29:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Through the energy fields, energy points, energy parameters.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.39,1:29:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.39,1:30:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.39,1:30:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.39,1:30:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It works through the energy meridians, is what it works through, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.39,1:30:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I've had very good experience with acupuncture.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.44,1:30:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Cured a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.44,1:30:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.44,1:30:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.44,1:30:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.44,1:30:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.20,1:30:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.49,1:30:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.49,1:30:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.49,1:30:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.49,1:30:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.49,1:30:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.49,1:30:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.79,1:30:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.79,1:30:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.79,1:30:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.79,1:30:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.87,1:30:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.89,1:30:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You've cured a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.89,1:30:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.42,1:30:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did this?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.58,1:30:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.58,1:30:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.06,1:30:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.06,1:30:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's great.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.06,1:30:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a drawing, a pencil drawing, a dot.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.25,1:31:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good, David.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.25,1:31:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.51,1:31:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.51,1:31:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.97,1:31:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because you're special.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.97,1:31:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That is lovely.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.19,1:31:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from Korea to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.47,1:31:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.99,1:31:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.07,1:31:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She says, may I have your blessing
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.98,1:31:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,for using my creative art to advance my spiritual growth?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.04,1:31:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you have my blessing to do so.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.70,1:31:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.02,1:31:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything subserves our spiritual growth
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.62,1:31:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,when we reach a certain level.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.72,1:31:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.80,1:31:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.06,1:32:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.48,1:32:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very pretty.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.76,1:32:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I call a picture of myself pretty.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.10,1:32:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because everything looks pretty.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.10,1:32:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.88,1:32:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.30,1:32:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Doc. Hi, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.48,1:32:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to clean up my side of the street.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.98,1:32:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Here to what?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.70,1:32:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Clean up my side of the street with the organization
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.50,1:32:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and you, Doc, and the spiritual community.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.24,1:32:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I had some inner emails with you and Donna,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.88,1:32:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was calling Doc by his first name,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.58,1:32:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and you said that that was disrespectful.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.86,1:32:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't my intention, and I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.94,1:32:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the adolescent in you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.46,1:32:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.22,1:32:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hanging around with Randy,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.72,1:33:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and I figured if I'm with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.02,1:33:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Randy, you know Randy.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.60,1:33:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Randy?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.54,1:33:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're Randy.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.48,1:33:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.02,1:33:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And so he calls you that all the time,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.66,1:33:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and I figured I would be closer by doing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.50,1:33:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But he asked before he was Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.90,1:33:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.52,1:33:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He knew Randy.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.11,1:33:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Before he was what?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.37,1:33:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.71,1:33:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.19,1:33:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.51,1:33:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.78,1:33:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.08,1:33:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.92,1:33:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it kind of put me in a prideful bear
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.02,1:33:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,than everybody else, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.68,1:33:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,because I could do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.12,1:33:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And so that was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.87,1:33:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't even like me calling you that,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.43,1:33:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm not calling you Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.45,1:33:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I draw the line.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.83,1:33:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.77,1:33:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I had a question about,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.19,1:34:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,he's into,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.41,1:34:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,he's into human design and he's kind of teaching me that.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.45,1:34:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you would calibrate that.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.43,1:34:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Human design?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.51,1:34:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.65,1:34:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know what,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.88,1:34:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,how can I calibrate something that I don't,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.99,1:34:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I could.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.01,1:34:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, I just,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:16.03,1:34:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know if it's good to, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.11,1:34:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.95,1:34:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Human design.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.03,1:34:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.35,1:34:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't either.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.97,1:34:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just an abstraction,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.41,1:34:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,intellectual abstraction.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.47,1:34:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.78,1:34:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to know it in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.60,1:34:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.96,1:34:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I let it go?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.34,1:34:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.64,1:34:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.12,1:34:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget you even thought of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.78,1:34:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,About what crystals do or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.69,1:34:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an intellectual.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.12,1:34:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like 400 type.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.24,1:34:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.70,1:34:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.68,1:34:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but I mean,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.50,1:34:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just like something that you learn about
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.88,1:35:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that I don't know that it has any power.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.80,1:35:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.52,1:35:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a natural curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.98,1:35:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.86,1:35:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.72,1:35:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the story you tell
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.76,1:35:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,about the engine going down the track?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.56,1:35:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one thing you need to know.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.62,1:35:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only what?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.60,1:35:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing you need to know about the buttons that you get.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.00,1:35:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.05,1:35:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.67,1:35:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.21,1:35:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.19,1:35:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.53,1:35:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I had my question.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.99,1:35:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.05,1:35:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.69,1:35:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I had my question, and it's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.69,1:35:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I, in my meditation, have fallen to a deep pit of despair.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.73,1:35:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop meditating.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.77,1:35:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.10,1:35:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.17,1:35:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So what should he do instead?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.45,1:35:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Pray?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.19,1:35:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.49,1:35:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.57,1:36:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Meditation doesn't work for everybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.49,1:36:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it doesn't work for you, then pray.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.23,1:36:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's many other things you can do.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.11,1:36:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You can walk the, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.27,1:36:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.61,1:36:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You can walk the labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.77,1:36:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.07,1:36:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So for him, it's better to walk the labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.39,1:36:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.99,1:36:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's other things you can do that are spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.91,1:36:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.39,1:36:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.73,1:36:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.55,1:36:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.26,1:36:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.54,1:36:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Many other things you can do.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.74,1:36:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You can dedicate everything you do to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.70,1:36:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you can, here, he wants to touch my hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.54,1:36:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.60,1:36:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.70,1:36:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.76,1:36:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.82,1:36:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.88,1:36:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.94,1:36:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.00,1:36:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.06,1:36:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.12,1:36:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.18,1:36:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.24,1:36:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.30,1:36:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.34,1:36:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.40,1:36:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.50,1:36:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.54,1:36:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.60,1:36:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.62,1:36:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.64,1:36:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.68,1:36:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.70,1:36:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You can, what did you say you can do?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.48,1:36:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You can dedicate anything, everything you do to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.30,1:36:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.80,1:36:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You can, you know, if you're digging in the garden, you say, dear God, I do this, and
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.30,1:36:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,thanks for my humanness and my life, and I do it for the good of the garden.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.22,1:36:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I do it for the good of the people who get fed by the food.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.70,1:36:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I do it out of love for my surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.78,1:37:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I love our bunnies.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.17,1:37:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You got wild bunnies?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.25,1:37:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I love them.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.75,1:37:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wild bunnies.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.32,1:37:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And I love my wild bunnies.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.74,1:37:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My dog likes me too. She loves chasing them. I'm just a take off after the rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.48,1:37:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi Susan and Dr. Hawkins. I talked to you last in I think 99 when you came to Seattle.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.48,1:37:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.48,1:37:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we were in Seattle in 99.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.48,1:37:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We were what?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.48,1:37:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We were in Seattle, Washington in 99. Remember that?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.87,1:37:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say so.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.87,1:37:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to thank God for Dr. Hawkins and the work that's come through him.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.87,1:37:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had a question but I think it has been answered and can I ask permission?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.87,1:37:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I ask it anyway for the highest good of everybody?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.87,1:38:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.57,1:38:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so what's been on my heart lately is I have a deep love for my country and I don't like the way it's going.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.80,1:38:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to be...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.80,1:38:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've been doing the reflection on the work that you put out and trying to elevate my consciousness as much as I can.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.80,1:38:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And I pray for those in power at night and say the Lord's Prayer.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.80,1:38:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm just wondering if it seems like there's being and then as long as I'm here should I be doing something to help?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.12,1:38:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And what could we do?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.12,1:38:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,To help?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.12,1:38:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,To help?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.37,1:38:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to help the United States of America. Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.37,1:38:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to help it?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.32,1:38:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.32,1:38:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's God's will.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.32,1:38:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you going to help it?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.32,1:38:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to know what his will is in my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.32,1:39:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A clear connection and awareness of his will and the capacity to carry out his will.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.61,1:39:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So how are you going to help your country?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.25,1:39:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I would surrender at your feet and ask for his help in my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.25,1:39:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you going to help your country, I ask you?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.25,1:39:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I have some ideas that come to me and I feel maybe I should act on them and...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.25,1:39:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So should we ask the question whether or not he should act on some of the ideas that he has?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.25,1:39:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.28,1:39:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.28,1:39:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And what way do you want to help your country?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.28,1:39:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop being vague and general.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.28,1:39:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to be a good guy and help the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.28,1:39:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.28,1:39:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And in what way?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.28,1:39:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweep the walk or invent a new buzz buzz or what?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.28,1:39:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So invention and ideas are something that come easy to me and...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.28,1:39:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.28,1:39:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had an experience with some fellows building a robot for a contest.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.28,1:39:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Building a robot?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.28,1:40:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.28,1:40:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.28,1:40:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,For a NASA contest.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.28,1:40:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Robot for what?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.34,1:40:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A NASA contest.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.34,1:40:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, it would, you know, they're using robotics now.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.34,1:40:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.34,1:40:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Robotics.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.34,1:40:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.34,1:40:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.34,1:40:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And in doing that, it was a great experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.34,1:40:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a great experience with my fellows and camaraderie and I would like to reinitiate that spirit of entrepreneurship in our country and do that by leading by example and maybe have a group of guys like that that might have a, live in a community with like a central shop where, you know, there's tools that we can use that none of us could afford by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.34,1:40:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, go ahead and do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.34,1:40:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.34,1:40:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.34,1:40:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.34,1:40:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.66,1:40:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.66,1:40:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I got what he's asking.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.88,1:40:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.88,1:40:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.52,1:40:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's the best way to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.52,1:40:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.52,1:40:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Have your creativity subserve the common good.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.52,1:40:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.52,1:41:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.52,1:41:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.22,1:41:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I just, I wanted to say thank you very much for all that you've done for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.22,1:41:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very grateful.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.22,1:41:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.22,1:41:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.22,1:41:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I can do about that life, so I have to live with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.40,1:41:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey, they can't film you, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.82,1:41:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.82,1:41:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.82,1:41:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.24,1:41:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.24,1:41:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.24,1:41:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.07,1:41:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.07,1:41:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.07,1:41:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.93,1:41:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.93,1:41:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.68,1:41:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.68,1:41:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.68,1:41:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.42,1:41:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.42,1:41:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.42,1:41:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.73,1:41:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll live with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.73,1:41:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.69,1:41:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I got to live with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.69,1:42:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Got to live with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.96,1:42:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Like taxes, the government.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.96,1:42:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.96,1:42:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.96,1:42:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My son, Jimmy, and thousands of other people in the world suffer from stuttering and
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.76,1:42:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,this...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.76,1:42:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Suffer from stuttering.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.76,1:42:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.76,1:42:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.76,1:42:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.76,1:42:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.76,1:42:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.76,1:42:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no known cause of it, and there's no known cure.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.76,1:42:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't do...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.76,1:42:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, have you tried hypnosis?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.76,1:42:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.76,1:42:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.76,1:42:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very effective.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.46,1:42:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.46,1:42:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, hypnosis has been pretty good with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.78,1:43:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we have about five minutes left, so let's try and keep the questions short so we can maybe get a few more in.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.88,1:43:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you could verify some suspicions I've had about my past lives.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.52,1:43:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to get into your past lives.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.90,1:43:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My first one was Plato.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.03,1:43:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.41,1:43:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Plato.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.21,1:43:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's his question?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.21,1:43:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If you could test if I was Plato.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.21,1:43:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you weren't Plato.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:37.21,1:43:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He was not Plato.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.38,1:43:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were Plato, you wouldn't be asking were you Plato.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.38,1:43:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Some idiot.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.72,1:43:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had some very deep cries about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.72,1:44:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.85,1:44:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had some very deep cries about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.85,1:44:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.52,1:44:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Cries?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.52,1:44:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he talking about? Please speak English. Speak up.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.65,1:44:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You were not Plato in a previous life.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.68,1:44:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,In a previous life, no. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.12,1:44:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you do some other past lives? Leonardo da Vinci?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.28,1:44:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He was Leonardo da Vinci in a past life. Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.57,1:44:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.57,1:44:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't Jesus Christ either. That'll save you asking.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.25,1:44:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.25,1:44:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of grandiosity with you, boy. Give up the grandiosity.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.51,1:44:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.51,1:44:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up the grandiosity, I said.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.51,1:44:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.99,1:44:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not the world's great genius.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.15,1:44:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The world doesn't need another genius.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.15,1:44:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's suffering from all past geniuses.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.15,1:45:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Give the world a break and be ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.68,1:45:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Be loving, kind, gentle, do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.68,1:45:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Look after your own responsibilities, pick up your own messes.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.26,1:45:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you can do for the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:11.45,1:45:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The world's full of people that want to be great, you know, that's cheap and...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.60,1:45:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.60,1:45:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you calibrate me, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.60,1:45:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrate you? Do we calibrate people?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.60,1:45:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.60,1:45:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we don't calibrate people.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.60,1:45:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't do it in a public setting.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.60,1:45:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.60,1:45:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's too much stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.80,1:45:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's not accurate.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.80,1:45:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have to do it in a private setting?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.80,1:45:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.83,1:45:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.24,1:45:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't, like, calibrate people.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.47,1:45:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.50,1:45:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My request was a similar one, but to Carl Jung, and that's all I want.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.88,1:45:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He thought he was Carl Jung.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.88,1:45:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Jung?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.88,1:45:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.88,1:45:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He thought he was Carl Jung.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.88,1:45:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.88,1:45:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no end to grandiosity.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.88,1:45:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.88,1:45:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Carl Jung.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.88,1:45:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.88,1:45:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:54.88,1:46:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it wouldn't do you any good if it was in your past life anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.20,1:46:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if these things were true in your past life, it wouldn't do you one iota of good.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.10,1:46:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It would just make you grandiose and arrogant.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.39,1:46:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I was Aristotle.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.92,1:46:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I was Plato.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.34,1:46:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.92,1:46:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to meet Joe Blow who goes to work every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.92,1:46:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It was real and genuine.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.17,1:46:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it won't do you any good.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.17,1:46:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Past lives don't mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.52,1:46:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Past lives don't mean anything as far as your current reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.52,1:46:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Your current reality of what you are now.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.52,1:46:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.56,1:46:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.97,1:46:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.97,1:46:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants you to calibrate him to tell him he wasn't Carl Jung.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.97,1:46:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to know if he was Carl Jung?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.97,1:46:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He was not Carl Jung.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.97,1:46:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants you to test with the arm.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.97,1:46:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.97,1:46:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.97,1:46:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He was not Carl Jung.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.97,1:46:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.97,1:47:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.90,1:47:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.90,1:47:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.93,1:47:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.93,1:47:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.93,1:47:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Move along.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:11.93,1:47:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Move along.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.93,1:47:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.93,1:47:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,One more and then that's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.89,1:47:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.89,1:47:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 1230.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.89,1:47:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.64,1:47:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.90,1:47:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.90,1:47:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.90,1:47:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a question but it seems like it's already been answered.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.90,1:47:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.90,1:47:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So I would just like to thank you both very much for your inspiration and I would like
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.90,1:47:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to shake your hand as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.90,1:47:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.90,1:47:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.90,1:47:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.96,1:47:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.96,1:47:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.24,1:47:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:50.10,1:47:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Any?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:52.35,1:47:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.64,1:48:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.44,1:48:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to say a few words.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.44,1:48:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.44,1:48:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,God's love is the law of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.27,1:48:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It is by His love that we live and breathe.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:19.36,1:48:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing exists except divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.95,1:48:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the only reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.95,1:48:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So we have to accept the divinity of our own creation.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.72,1:48:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank the Lord God for my life.
